        },
        "x-ms-visibility": "important",
        "summary": "Convert Invoice to ZUGFeRD PDF",
        "description": "Creates a fully compliant ZUGFeRD PDF/A-3 invoice by embedding structured invoice data (XML) into a readable PDF. Supports the ZUGFeRD standard (EN 16931) and generates hybrid PDF/A-3 documents suitable for digital archiving and electronic invoice exchange - https://support.power2apps.de/T10_BillConverter/t10-a001-av01-cv01-convertinvoicetozugferdpdf"
      }
    },
